originalText.text: Shameless and rude organization who like to exploit parents' love for their children to make money. Additionally, at the Orlando world's competition the organization representative at the front door had some choice words, while children were present. Disorganized, sessions started late and on several occasions the music for the floor exercise cut out leaving the kids to complete their routines without music. When dealing with them  be prepared to pay registration fees for the child, entry fee to see your child and then if your child is invited to compete for finals (even if it is for just one event) they will request another entrance fee. No wonder they schedule the finals on a different day.
